<div class="sect2">
<h3 id="30">2.1. Secure Invoice</h3>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>You need a separate <strong>Portal ID</strong> and <strong>Key</strong> for the payment method <strong>Secure Invoice</strong>. This Portal-ID and this key have to be deposited in the plugin in the <strong>Secure Invoice</strong> area while configuring it. You get the Portal ID and the Key via the Payone Merchant Interface in the <strong>Configuration » Payment portals</strong> menu.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="sect2">
<h3 id="40">2.2. Credit card</h3>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>The payment method <strong>Credit card</strong> is a special case. Additional settings are needed for this payment method. These are described in <a href="#table-settings-credit-card">Table 3</a>.</p>
</div>
